high_descs: Take a step forward, then turn left and walk across the room to the window, once at the window turn left to face the wooden dresser.
Pick up the phone that is in between the pencil and the disk on the wooden dresser.
Turn left and walk over to the end of the bed.
Place the phone on the bed to the right of the laptop.
Turn left and walk back over to the wooden dresser.
Pick up the phone that still remains on the wooden dresser.
Turn left and walk back over to the end of the bed.
Place the phone on the bed to the right of the phone that is already on the bed.
anns.task_desc: Move two phones to a bed.

high_descs: turn left and walk to the end of the room, then turn left and face the right side of the dresser
pick the cellphone up off of the dresser
turn left and walk to the foot of the bed, turn left to face the foot of the bed
place the cellphone down on top of the bed to the right of the laptop
turn left and walk to the end of the room, then turn left to face the dresser again
pick the second cellphone up off of the dresser
turn left and walk to the foot of the bed, turn left to face the foot of the bed
place the cellphone down on the bed to the right of the other cellphone to the right of the laptop
anns.task_desc: place two cellphones down at the foot of the bed

high_descs: Move forward, turn left to go toward the window, then turn left to face the dresser.
Pick up the cell phone on the dresser, located in front of the CD.
Turn left, go straight, then turn left to face the bed.
Put the cell phone on the bed, to the right of the computer.
Turn left, go straight, then turn left to turn to the dresser.
Pick up the cell phone from the dresser.
Turn left, go forward, then turn left to face the bed.
Put the cell phone on the bed, to the right of the other cell phone.
anns.task_desc: Put two cell phones on the bed.

high_descs: go to window to the left, face dresser to left of window
pick up cell phone in between pencil and CD
go to the bed with laptop
place cell phone on bed on right side of laptop by touchpad
go to dresser next to window
pick up cell phone from front, right side of dresser
go to bed with laptop
place cell phone to the right of other cell phone on the bed
anns.task_desc: place two cell phones next to laptop on the bed

high_descs: Cross the room to stand at the end of the dresser that's closest to the window.
Pick up the cell phone from the dresser that's closest to the laptop.
Carry the cell phone to the bed.
Place the phone on the bed by the laptop.
Return to the dresser at the end closest to the window.
Pick up the other phone from the dresser.
Carry the phone over to the foot of the bed again.
Place the phone to the right of the other phone you previously placed there.
anns.task_desc: Move two cell phones to the bed.

high_descs: Turn left towards the window and turn left to face the desk.
Pick up the cell phone farthest from you.
Turn left and walk towards the computer on the bed to your left.
Place the cell phone to the right of the computer.
Turn around, walk towards the window, and turn left to face the desk.
Pick up the cell phone from the desk.
Turn left and walk towards the computer on the bed to your left.
Place the cell phone to the right of the other cell phone on the bed.
anns.task_desc: Place the two cell phones from the desk to the bed.
